text: Agnee Morcha is a Hindi action movie from Bollywood starring Dharmendra, Ravi Kishan, Mukesh Khanna, directed by Raju Chouhan and produced by Rajesh Kothari. The film was released on 4 April 1997 under the banner of Shiva Dolly Films. == Cast == * Dharmendra * Mukesh Khanna * Ravi Kishan * Simran * Johnny lever * Raza Murad * Mushtaq Khan == References == == Other websites == * Category:1997 movies Category:1990s Indian movies
